[ul][list][list][list][list][center][Img]http://i29.tinypic.com/2u6mw02.png[/img][/center] [center][img]http://s4.tinypic.com/10dfnnc_th.jpg[/img] [size=20pt][b]Number one In RSPS Packs[/b][/size][/center] [center][b][i]What is ZodiacsReign?[/i] [b][font=Verdana]ZodiacsReign is a RSPS helper containing mostly required programs and files to make your RSPS coding and playing more proficient and easy, Zodiacsreign has been around for almost 2 years and I've been updating for a very long time. In "ZodiacsReign Packages" you will find Tools, Id List , Essentials to make your private server experience a better one.[/b][/center] [color=maroon] [center][b][i] [color=blue]In the new ZodiacsReign 9.0, This is the anniversary edition, I had no idea what to add to this to make it special, But the fact is that today is the day I released ZodiacsReign into the RSPS World. Thank you for downloading this if you did. [/b][/center]
[Center][size=20pt]Download Link~[/size] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/vxja6e.jpg[/img] http://www.mediafire.com/?lzyzwzkwnnm[b] 17.55mb[/b] [img]http://www.mediafire.com/free-file-hosting/mediafire-swoosh.gif[/img] [/center]
